snippet: Douglas Costa's unstoppable 25-metre strike was enough to give lacklustre Bayern Munich a 1-0 victory over bottom side Darmstadt 98 on Sunday and put the champions back on top of the Bundesliga....
lead_paragraph: Douglas Costa's unstoppable 25-metre strike was enough to give lacklustre Bayern Munich a 1-0 victory over bottom side Darmstadt 98 on Sunday and put the champions back on top of the Bundesliga.

headline.main: Costa Missile Sends Bayern Back to Top of the Bundesliga
headline.print_headline: Costa Missile Sends Bayern Back to Top of the Bundesliga
